import Nav from 'react-bootstrap/Nav';
import '../App.css'

const HeaderComponent = () => {
    return (
        <Nav className="justify-content-center bg-dark " activeKey="/home">
        <Nav.Item>
          <Nav.Link href="/" id = "Hello" class = "fs-3 px-2 mt-0 text-light ">Home</Nav.Link>
        </Nav.Item>
        <Nav.Item>
          <Nav.Link href="/projects" id = "Hello" class = "fs-3 px-2 mt-0 fst-italic text-light">Projects</Nav.Link>
        </Nav.Item>
        <Nav.Item>
          <Nav.Link href="/contact" id = "Hello" class = "fs-3 px-2 mt-0 fst-italic text-light">Contact</Nav.Link>
        </Nav.Item>
        <Nav.Item>
          <Nav.Link href="/about" id = "Hello" class = "fs-3 px-2 mt-0 fst-italic text-light">
            About
          </Nav.Link>
        </Nav.Item>
      </Nav>
    )
}

export default HeaderComponent
